NetworkManager-vpn: NetworkManager (NetworkManager VPN Extensions)
NetworkManager-vpn:
NetworkManager-vpn: NetworkManager-vpn attempts to make networking invisible. When moving 
NetworkManager-vpn: into areas you've been before, NetworkManager-vpn automatically connects 
NetworkManager-vpn: to the last network the user chose to connect to. Likewise, when 
NetworkManager-vpn: back at the desk, NetworkManager-vpn will switch to the faster, more 
NetworkManager-vpn: reliable wired network connection. 
NetworkManager-vpn:
NetworkManager-vpn: This package provides NetworkManager with VPN Extensions for
NetworkManager-vpn: openvpn and vpnc.
NetworkManager-vpn:
